/**
 * REZ Ecosystem - Unified Integration Hub
 *
 * Central module connecting all companies and services
 *
 * Connects:
 * - RABTUL Infrastructure (Auth, Payment, Wallet, etc.)
 * - REZ Intelligence (AI/ML services)
 * - REZ Media (Ads, Karma, Attribution)
 * - CorpPerks (HR, Benefits, Perks)
 * - REZ-Consumer (QR, Apps)
 * - REZ-Merchant (POS, KDS)
 * - StayOwn-Hospitality (Hotels)
 */

